{"type":"step-attempt","step":"request-review","sessionId":"30ee0670-1d24-4acb-99ad-bdef479bffed","outcome":{"verdict":"approve","findingsPath":"specrunner/changes/commit-projection-unify/request-review-result-001.md","error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"verdict":"approve","findings":[],"observations":[{"severity":"low","file":"src/core/step/commit-orchestrator.ts","title":"store.appendHistory の中間 disk write が projector 統合で暗黙に除去される","rationale":"store.appendHistory（job-journal.ts:208-212）は in-memory state 更新 + 中間 disk write の二役を担う。pure projector が history を in-memory append した後に store.appendHistory を呼ぶと history が二重追記される。round path では既に appendHistory を呼ばず最終 store.persist のみで完結しており、同パターンで統一すれば安全。commit message に意図的変更として明示すること。","line":178},{"severity":"low","file":"src/core/step/commit-orchestrator.ts","title":"commitSkipped の verdict:parsed emit が pre-persist から post-persist に変わる","rationale":"現在 commitSkipped（逐次）は verdict:parsed を store.persist より前に emit する（lines 291-298 → 300）。要件 2 の post-persist 共通ヘルパに skipped emit も含めると timing が pre→post に変わる。round path では既に post-persist emit であり設計意図に沿うが、厳密には挙動変更。実害なし。","line":291}]},"followUpAttempts":1,"transientRetryAttempts":0},"startedAt":"2026-07-14T04:22:17.378Z","endedAt":"2026-07-14T04:27:04.162Z"}
